T1  - Convergent Stakeholder Theory
AU  - Jones, Thomas M.
AU  - Wicks, Andrew C.
Y1  - 1999/04/01
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1999.1893929
DO  - 10.5465/amr.1999.1893929
